{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Ukrainian fellow was nice enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he would have be killed for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we walk back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was going on [INAUDIBLE] to Succos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Succos, unfortunately, the first day of Succos came around four [INAUDIBLE] with big-- that's always four German people, SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave an order to take all whatever is left, walking to the graves barefoot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them, they took the-- by trucks, most of them by foot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever couldn't walk, they were slaughtering with knives, with bullets, and threw them in the ditch all the way there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From Miedzyrzecz through Niewirko, it will say right in there, probably in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the place where they have buried the 3,000 men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Niewirko is the place that the Jewish men had a factory that they used to make stones, bricks, [BACKGROUND NOISE] full with sand-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] [INAUDIBLE] --and full with sand.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And what happened there, that's-- they were easy to dig.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were right in there starting to dig the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it took, I would say, around eight hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we dig the graves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And between the digging to graves was a lot of killing, a lot of scream.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because a lot of people didn't want to dig the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because they knew that they digging for themselves the graves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You have to make the grave like that, going down with steps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the top is a hill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's what-- my children saw it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We have a map of everything there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We drawed a map.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Like I mentioned before, my son is a beautiful city planner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was an architect, making all the design to make that stone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So you saw the beautiful view of mountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
